    "7f0e1a0b-48c1-44da-9052-455c13a7b5dd": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "template--15611813986348__7f0e1a0b-48c1-44da-9052-455c13a7b5dd-collapsible_row-1": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why Nam Nam Freeze Dried Candy?",
            "icon": "clipboard",
            "row_content": "<p>Ever wondered what happens when your favourite candy gets a makeover? Nam Nam's freeze drying magic turns ordinary candies into extraordinary, crunchy delights! 😋 Brace yourself for a taste bud adventure like never before!</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "1b197a56-0865-45b4-b205-7f7fdf5bc27f": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does the flavor change?",
            "icon": "clipboard",
            "row_content": "<p>Nope! It's a flavor explosion! Our freeze-drying process cranks up the intensity, making every bite a flavor-packed thrill ride. Prepare your taste buds for a symphony of deliciousness! 🤤</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "cf912be4-ba40-4535-96aa-13227ce9be79": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why the Splurge? 💸",
            "icon": "clipboard",
            "row_content": "<p>Because greatness takes time! It takes 8-12 hours to transform each batch into crispy perfection. Our top-notch equipment doesn't come cheap, but we're committed to offering you the finest freeze-dried treats at the best price. Treat yourself without breaking the bank! 🤑</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "a9893458-b2d9-4345-b5b8-694d6057fb87": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Hoping for fewer calories?",
            "icon": "clipboard",
            "row_content": "<p>Sorry, no shortcuts there! The puffiness might fool you, but the calorie count remains the same. Indulge guilt-free in our airy, freeze-dried wonders! </p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "fef0a8d5-8d96-4cee-bb63-7f8229b21ea0": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does it last?",
            "icon": "clipboard",
            "row_content": "<p>Well, that depends on your willpower! Seriously, though, our freeze-dried wonders can stick around for a minimum of a year if you keep them cool, dry, and away from prying hands. Our candies are so fresh that they hardly hang out on our shelves for more than 2-3 days! Want to extend the party? Throw in a couple of oxygen absorbers, and voilà—your treats are set for an extended shelf life! 😀</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
